metadata.name: Probably Nothing 001
metadata.description:
GENESIS collection consists of the first 100 seats in Probably Nothing School - a NFT launch course with Blake Jamieson.

Holding this token allows you access to a students-only discord channel.

https://discord.gg/probablynothing

A snapshot will be taken of all token holders on February 1, 2022 at 12:00AM EST.

For each GENESIS token held, users will be given one free mint pass* for the follow-along NFT project. Mint pass distribution date TBD.

Visit https://probablynothing.school for more info

*mint pass redeemable for one free NFT, but user responsible for paying gas fees
